{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_01","textHome":"啊……好累……@这种日子还要上课，我想要出去活动身子啊！@光是听讲课，整个人就快瘫下去了，@眼皮也开始打架了……真的好累啊！@而且我完全就学不来这些。@决定了，下午的课就翘掉吧！@怎么样？不许告诉千里哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_18","textHome":"之前我们玩了打僵尸的游戏，千里她超害怕～@就算她一直在逞强，但时不时还会暴露出来！@哈哈！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_19","textHome":"这就是魔法少女的力量！@嗯嗯，感觉很棒吧！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_20","textHome":"嗯呜！哈啊……感觉终于清醒了。@爽快！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_21","textHome":"成为魔法少女时祈求的“力量”，@也没能改变我孤零零一个人的事实。@在遇到千里之后，我似乎发生了改变……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_22","textHome":"对于接受我作为同伴的大家，@我想要为她们做些什么。@不过我不擅长思考，可能要花上很多时间……@但我会试着想想用我的“力量”能做些什么。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_23","textHome":"一个人做不到的事，和同伴一起就能做到……@而且能让自己变得更强……这是千里教我的。@千里她们就是我的同伴，我不再是一个人了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_24","textHome":"来得也太晚啦！你到底跑哪乱逛去了！？@嘛，算了。总之……能先帮我写一下作业吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_25","textHome":"咕……呜喵呜喵……@嗯？早上……不对，还没到早上呢……@明明才刚睡一会儿……呼……呜喵呜喵……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_26","textHome":"啊～我饿了！@不行了！撑不住了。完全听不了课了。@溜出去找便利店吧！想想，吃什么好呢♪"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_27","textHome":"终于结束了～@只不过是翘了几节课，没有去考试而已，@老师就一直训个不停……他还真是顽固啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_03","textHome":"千里真是的……@又让我想起了那个时候的事情……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_28","textHome":"我决定了……我要把这部漫画全卷都看完！@虽然有150卷，但给我一个晚上就足够了！@别小看我哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":200}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_29","textHome":"我的布丁不见了！？@谁，是谁……是哪个家伙偷了我的布丁！？@不过这就和我吃了爸爸和妈妈的布丁一样吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_30","textHome":"接下来，该一个人巡逻去了。@你在害怕个什么劲啊。@要是有敌人出现，我就会马上干掉它的，@所以放心！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_31","textHome":"嗯。竟然有这么不可思议的地方～@详细情况我也不懂！@总之把我们的复制品统统干掉吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_32","textHome":"有这么多的魔法少女，稍微有些害怕呢……@你觉得我会这么说吗！？笨～蛋！@只要像平常一样不就行了嘛！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":1}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_33","textHome":"真走运！今天上午就放学了！@现在去哪好呢～！？@找茉莉一起逛街去吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_34","textHome":"昨天，在机厅呆到了很晚，@可能要被叫去训话了。@我竟然会犯这样的错误，真是大意了啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_35","textHome":"用必杀技的话，我就会损耗相当大的体力……@不过，要是舍不得出招的话，@能赢的战斗也会赢不了的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_36","textHome":"反击之后的连招攻击！@趁对方落脚未稳，蓄力发动必杀技！@KO！嗯嗯，这就是胜利的法则！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_37","textHome":"过去，我是个超阴暗又早熟的家伙。@嘛，还是有些可爱的吧？@看现在的我是没办法想象的啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_04","textHome":"即使那样……呜……@我也依旧是活力满满！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_38","textHome":"成为魔法少女之后我变强了，@也能争口气给大家看看了！@不过，总感觉和自己期待的东西有些不同……@一直都是如此。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_39","textHome":"说实话，我很不擅长和人相处。@不过多亏了千里，我改变了。@那个时候，能握住千里的手真是太好了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"id":403300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_40","textHome":"四个人一起协力战斗的时候，@我能安心地感觉到自己不再是一个人……@我会用我的力量，来守护我的容身之地……@来守护那三个人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_41","textHome":"昨天巡逻巡得太晚了，今天起床好吃力啊～@虽说每天早上起床都很难就是了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_42","textHome":"今天也来大干一场吧！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_43","textHome":"啊～～～好无聊……"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_44","textHome":"早点回去洗个澡吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_45","textHome":"这么弱还敢来找事。"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_46","textHome":"看来我有些太强了呢！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_63","textHome":"最大出力！！"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_05","textHome":"之后我们也要在一……@干、干嘛，你有什么意见吗！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_64","textHome":"不要再装乖了！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_65","textHome":"我就会让你后悔惹上我的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":403300,"motion":400}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_66","textHome":"不觉得很蠢吗！？"}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_02","textHome":"我是成见亚里纱！@在学校里，似乎是有名的不良少女……@啊！等等！我什么都不会做的所以不要害怕！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_13","textHome":"嗯，状态不错♪@那么！就照这样变得更强吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_14","textHome":"诶……等等，真的吗！？@哈……我已经是最强的了！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_15","textHome":"啊，刚刚那个……感觉好棒！@看来你还是挺可靠的嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_16","textHome":"我啊，虽然学习完全不在行，@但打起游戏可是一绝哦。@最近，还在格斗游戏里@把让我不爽的家伙好好教训了一顿呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_17","textHome":"之前被我在游戏里打得落花流水的家伙，@最近似乎变强了。@不过，再怎么特训都是一样的！@下次也要打败他！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403300,"motion":100}]}]},"version":3}